item.title: sdwdate preparation not successfull
item.dc:creator: Patrick
item.description:
That’s really the full log? Nothing else?

If yes, for debugging, please run and post output here:

sudo -u sdwdate /usr/libexec/helper-scripts/onion-time-pre-script

Is there something really broken or are you just worried about “(known) ERROR”?
If yes, don’t be worried and see: Support Request Policy.

Any connectivity issues? If yes, see:

Whonix – 20 Jun 22
